{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017DkY8QvZY8miEnzDBKs7j7","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→#!/bin/bash\n     2→# llm-eval: Haiku 4.5로 에이전트 추천 후 지시\n     3→\n     4→MODEL=\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\"\n     5→\n     6→INPUT_JSON=$(timeout 2 cat || echo '{}')\n     7→USER_PROMPT=$(echo \"$INPUT_JSON\" | jq -r '.prompt // \"\"' 2>/dev/null)\n     8→CWD=$(echo \"$INPUT_JSON\" | jq -r '.cwd // \"\"' 2>/dev/null)\n     9→\n    10→if [ -z \"$CWD\" ] || [ \"$CWD\" = \"null\" ]; then\n    11→  CWD=\"${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR:-.}\"\n    12→fi\n    13→\n    14→# .claude/agents/*.md에서 description 추출\n    15→AGENTS_DIR=\"$CWD/.claude/agents\"\n    16→AGENT_LIST=\"\"\n    17→\n    18→if [ -d \"$AGENTS_DIR\" ]; then\n    19→  for agent_file in \"$AGENTS_DIR\"/*.md; do\n    20→    [ -f \"$agent_file\" ] || continue\n    21→    agent_name=$(basename \"$agent_file\" .md)\n    22→    agent_desc=$(sed -n '/^---$/,/^---$/p' \"$agent_file\" | grep '^description:' | sed 's/^description: *//' | head -n 1)\n    23→    if [ -n \"$agent_desc\" ]; then\n    24→      AGENT_LIST=\"${AGENT_LIST}- ${agent_name}: ${agent_desc}\n    25→\"\n    26→    fi\n    27→  done\n    28→fi\n    29→\n    30→FALLBACK=\"INSTRUCTION: Task 위임 시 .claude/agents/의 에이전트 설명을 참고하여 적합한 에이전트를 선택하세요.\"\n    31→\n    32→if [ -z \"$ANTHROPIC_API_KEY\" ]; then\n    33→  echo \"$FALLBACK\"\n    34→  exit 0\n    35→fi\n    36→\n    37→EVAL_PROMPT=$(cat <<EOF\n    38→사용자 요청에 가장 적합한 에이전트를 하나만 선택하세요.\n    39→\n    40→요청: ${USER_PROMPT}\n    41→\n    42→에이전트 목록:\n    43→${AGENT_LIST}\n    44→에이전트 이름만 반환하세요 (예: db-query-helper). 적합한 에이전트가 없으면 none을 반환하세요.\n    45→EOF\n    46→)\n    47→\n    48→RESPONSE=$(curl -s --max-time 15 https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages \\\n    49→  -H \"content-type: application/json\" \\\n    50→  -H \"x-api-key: $ANTHROPIC_API_KEY\" \\\n    51→  -H \"anthropic-version: 2023-06-01\" \\\n    52→  -d \"{\n    53→    \\\"model\\\": \\\"$MODEL\\\",\n    54→    \\\"max_tokens\\\": 100,\n    55→    \\\"temperature\\\": 0,\n    56→    \\\"system\\\": \\\"You are an agent router. Return only the agent name, nothing else.\\\",\n    57→    \\\"messages\\\": [{\n    58→      \\\"role\\\": \\\"user\\\",\n    59→      \\\"content\\\": $(echo \"$EVAL_PROMPT\" | jq -Rs .)\n    60→    }]\n    61→  }\")\n    62→\n    63→AGENT_NAME=$(echo \"$RESPONSE\" | jq -r '.content[0].text' 2>/dev/null | tr -d '[:space:]' | tr -d '\"')\n    64→\n    65→if [ -z \"$AGENT_NAME\" ] || [ \"$AGENT_NAME\" = \"null\" ] || [ \"$AGENT_NAME\" = \"none\" ]; then\n    66→  echo \"$FALLBACK\"\n    67→else\n    68→  echo \"INSTRUCTION: LLM 평가 결과, 이 작업에 가장 적합한 에이전트는 \\\"${AGENT_NAME}\\\"입니다.\"\n    69→  echo \"\"\n    70→  echo \"반드시 Task(subagent_type=\\\"${AGENT_NAME}\\\")로 위임하세요.\"\n    71→fi\n    72→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Rrkw7ubE2zbCLkVHAwgPhR","session_id":"ef67a638-87a8-4ae9-8866-e5521c6e89e6","uuid":"601f26a8-d5ab-47bd-badd-734f12128786"}
